label: Shenzhen Economic Daily
title: Shenzhen_Economic_Daily
exrest: The Shenzhen Economic Daily, alternatively translated as Shenzhen Business Post, Shenzhen Commercial Daily, Shenzhen Business News, is a large comprehensive daily newspaper with economic reporting as its main focus, and is the party newspaper directly under the Shenzhen Municipal Committee of the Chinese Communist Party. The newspaper was launched on January 8, 1989, and is divided into four sections: "News Section", "Economy Section", "Recreation Section" and "Market Section".
